<subSubSection id="C3216524FFDAFFA7FF43FA66FBBFF8A4" pageId="3" pageNumber="183" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="8B8436AFFFDAFFA7FF43FA66FBBFF8A4" blockId="3.[136,1452,1526,1877]" pageId="3" pageNumber="183">
In the protologue of 
<taxonomicName id="4C3B4D2CFFDAFFA7FEBAFA66FDD6F9E1" authorityName="Pohl" authorityYear="1833" box="[369,541,1526,1552]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Malvaceae" genus="Luehea" kingdom="Plantae" order="Malvales" pageId="3" pageNumber="183" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="macrophylla">
<emphasis id="B94FEABDFFDAFFA7FEBAFA66FDD6F9E1" box="[369,541,1526,1552]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="183">L. macrophylla</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
no reference is made to a specific specimen. Pohl’s original collection is kept in W where he worked and lived (
<bibRefCitation id="EFAA4B5EFFDAFFA7FE27F98BFD3FF9C5" author="Stafleu, F. A. &amp; Cowan, R. S." box="[492,756,1562,1588]" pageId="3" pageNumber="183" refId="ref8497" refString="Stafleu, F. A. &amp; Cowan, R. S. (1976 - 1988) Taxonomic Literature: A selective guide to botanical publications and collections with dates, commentaries and types, 2 nd ed., Smithsonian Libraries, last updated 28 Jun. 2012. https: // doi. org / 10.5962 / bhl. title. 48631" type="book" year="1976">Stafleu &amp; Cowan 1976</bibRefCitation>
–1988: 315). We found only 
<specimenCount id="9D3DFD26FFDAFFA7FBF2F98AFB2BF9C5" box="[1081,1248,1562,1589]" pageId="3" pageNumber="183" type="generic">two specimens</specimenCount>
of 
<location id="8EE46074FFDAFFA7FACDF98BFA87F9C5" LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:039287B9FFDAFFA7FF43FAD7FBBFF8A4:8EE46074FFDAFFA7FACDF98BFA87F9C5" box="[1286,1356,1562,1588]" country="Brazil" municipality="Both" name="Pohl's" pageId="3" pageNumber="183">Pohl’s</location>
original collection with the name 
<taxonomicName id="4C3B4D2CFFDAFFA7FE6BF9AEFD81F9A9" authorityName="Pohl" authorityYear="1833" box="[416,586,1598,1624]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Malvaceae" genus="Luehea" kingdom="Plantae" order="Malvales" pageId="3" pageNumber="183" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="macrophylla">
<emphasis id="B94FEABDFFDAFFA7FE6BF9AEFD81F9A9" box="[416,586,1598,1624]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="183">L. macrophylla</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
preserved in this herbarium. 
<collectingMunicipality id="6BE0ACD5FFDAFFA7FC44F9AFFC0EF9A9" box="[911,965,1598,1624]" pageId="3" pageNumber="183">Both</collectingMunicipality>
specimens were collected by 
<collectorName id="26CE5379FFDAFFA7FADAF9AFFA8FF9A9" box="[1297,1348,1598,1624]" pageId="3" pageNumber="183">Pohl</collectorName>
in 
<collectingCountry id="F32C763FFFDAFFA7FAACF9AFFA60F9A9" box="[1383,1451,1598,1624]" name="Brazil" pageId="3" pageNumber="183">Brazil</collectingCountry>
(
<collectorName id="26CE5379FFDAFFA7FF59F9F3FEE8F98D" box="[146,291,1634,1660]" pageId="3" pageNumber="183">B. Wallnöfer</collectorName>
, pers. comm.), and are 
<typeStatus id="5480880DFFDAFFA7FDECF9F2FD42F98C" box="[551,649,1635,1661]" pageId="3" pageNumber="183">syntypes</typeStatus>
of 
<taxonomicName id="4C3B4D2CFFDAFFA7FD65F9F2FC93F98D" authorityName="Pohl" authorityYear="1833" box="[686,856,1634,1660]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Malvaceae" genus="Luehea" kingdom="Plantae" order="Malvales" pageId="3" pageNumber="183" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="macrophylla">
<emphasis id="B94FEABDFFDAFFA7FD65F9F2FC93F98D" box="[686,856,1634,1660]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="183">L. macrophylla</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. They have labels mentioning the location congruent with the protologue, and Pohl’s handwriting (
<collectorName id="26CE5379FFDAFFA7FD5EF917FCE2F951" box="[661,809,1670,1696]" pageId="3" pageNumber="183">B. Wallnöfer</collectorName>
, pers. comm.), but the page and illustration numbers of the species publication are erroneous and correspond to the description and illustration of 
<taxonomicName id="4C3B4D2CFFDAFFA7FB41F93AFAE4F935" authorityName="Pohl" authorityYear="1833" box="[1162,1327,1706,1732]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Malvaceae" genus="Luehea" kingdom="Plantae" order="Malvales" pageId="3" pageNumber="183" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="microphylla">
<emphasis id="B94FEABDFFDAFFA7FB41F93AFAE4F935" box="[1162,1327,1706,1732]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="183">L. microphylla</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. However, these specimens are 
<taxonomicName id="4C3B4D2CFFDAFFA7FEA4F95EFDD2F919" authorityName="Pohl" authorityYear="1833" box="[367,537,1742,1768]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Malvaceae" genus="Luehea" kingdom="Plantae" order="Malvales" pageId="3" pageNumber="183" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="macrophylla">
<emphasis id="B94FEABDFFDAFFA7FEA4F95EFDD2F919" box="[367,537,1742,1768]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="183">L. macrophylla</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, and agree well with the vegetative and reproductive description presented in the protologue. For this reason, in accordance with Arts. 9.3 and 9.4 of the ICN, we have designated herein the specimen 
<emphasis id="B94FEABDFFDAFFA7FF43F887FF25F8C1" box="[136,238,1814,1840]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="183">Pohl s.n.</emphasis>
(W0071385) as the 
<typeStatus id="5480880DFFDAFFA7FE15F887FD8EF8C1" box="[478,581,1814,1840]" pageId="3" pageNumber="183">lectotype</typeStatus>
of 
<taxonomicName id="4C3B4D2CFFDAFFA7FDA4F886FCD7F8C1" authorityName="Pohl" authorityYear="1833" box="[623,796,1814,1840]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Malvaceae" genus="Luehea" kingdom="Plantae" order="Malvales" pageId="3" pageNumber="183" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="macrophylla">
<emphasis id="B94FEABDFFDAFFA7FDA4F886FCD7F8C1" box="[623,796,1814,1840]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="183">L. macrophylla</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, by choosing the most complete specimen. 
<collectorName id="26CE5379FFDAFFA7FAD2F887FA8EF8C1" box="[1305,1349,1814,1840]" pageId="3" pageNumber="183">The</collectorName>
name 
<taxonomicName id="4C3B4D2CFFDAFFA7FA5EF886FEDEF8A5" authorityName="Pohl" authorityYear="1833" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Malvaceae" genus="Luehea" kingdom="Plantae" order="Malvales" pageId="3" pageNumber="183" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="macrophylla">
<emphasis id="B94FEABDFFDAFFA7FA5EF886FEDEF8A5" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="183">L. macrophylla</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
has been considered a synonym of 
<taxonomicName id="4C3B4D2CFFDAFFA7FD68F8AAFCA2F8A5" authority="A. St." authorityName="A. St." box="[675,873,1850,1876]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Malvaceae" genus="Luehea" kingdom="Plantae" order="Malvales" pageId="3" pageNumber="183" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="rufescens">
<emphasis id="B94FEABDFFDAFFA7FD68F8AAFCE0F8A5" box="[675,811,1850,1876]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="183">L. rufescens</emphasis>
A.St.
</taxonomicName>
- 
<collectorName id="26CE5379FFDAFFA7FCBAF8ABFC55F8A5" box="[881,926,1850,1876]" pageId="3" pageNumber="183">Hil.</collectorName>
(
<bibRefCitation id="EFAA4B5EFFDAFFA7FC67F8ABFBACF8A4" author="Schumann, K." box="[940,1127,1850,1877]" pageId="3" pageNumber="183" pagination="117 - 200" refId="ref8376" refString="Schumann, K. (1886) Tilliaceae. Flora Brasiliensis, enumeratio plantarum in Brasilia hactenus detectarum: quas suis aliorumque botanicorum studiis descriptas et methodo naturali digestas partim icone illustratas 12 (3): 117 - 200. https: // doi. org / 10.5962 / bhl. title. 454" type="journal article" year="1886">Schumann 1886</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
